684
00:39:59,100 --> 00:40:00,840
<font color="yellow">We have different perspectives.</font>

685
00:40:02,800 --> 00:40:04,170
<font color="yellow">Ordinary people...</font>

686
00:40:04,700 --> 00:40:06,870
<font color="yellow">may consider this some sort of hope,</font>

687
00:40:07,400 --> 00:40:08,440
<font color="yellow">but I...</font>

688
00:40:09,700 --> 00:40:11,140
<font color="yellow">don't consider it as hope at all.</font>

689
00:40:15,510 --> 00:40:16,510
<font color="yellow">Here.</font>

