00:42:06,170 --> 00:42:07,540
<font color="yellow">This is exactly what I wanted.</font>

718
00:42:08,300 --> 00:42:09,340
<font color="yellow">We all...</font>

719
00:42:10,170 --> 00:42:12,100
<font color="yellow">need help from others.</font>

720
00:42:13,770 --> 00:42:14,770
<font color="yellow">It's not...</font>

721
00:42:16,100 --> 00:42:18,800
<font color="yellow">shameful to ask someone for help.</font>

722
00:42:22,040 --> 00:42:23,300
<font color="yellow">When you reach out for help,</font>

723
00:42:24,300 --> 00:42:26,100
<font color="yellow">I believe someone will help you.</font>

724
00:42:29,340 --> 00:42:31,100
<font color="yellow">That includes someone who's looking for a solution.</font>

725
00:42:45,040 --> 00:42:47,340
