<font color="yellow">It's late.</font>

728
00:43:56,240 --> 00:43:57,700
<font color="yellow">How are you going to take responsibility?</font>

729
00:43:58,340 --> 00:44:01,600
<font color="yellow">Do you know how hard it is for me to fall back asleep?</font>

730
00:44:02,240 --> 00:44:03,340
