747
00:45:02,600 --> 00:45:03,640
<font color="yellow">and...</font>

748
00:45:04,500 --> 00:45:05,500
<font color="yellow">illegal.</font>

749
00:45:06,300 --> 00:45:08,570
<font color="yellow">And the most important factor is money.</font>

750
00:45:09,270 --> 00:45:12,400
